Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 這種事
